sections.text:
The Minister may cancel an approval for suspension of duty onmanufacturing inputsif—
(a)the manufacturer sells to a person, or otherwise disposes of, themanufacturing inputsto which the suspension of duty relates;
(b)the rates of duty on themanufacturinginput become lower than the rates of duty on the comparable imported finished products;
(c)themanufacturing inputsto which the suspension of duty relates are used for a purpose other thanmanufacturing; or
(d)the approval for suspension of duty is used for any other purpose contrary to the purpose of these Regulations.
